      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Carpaint_header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/632783516/Lama_Carpaint_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761637160872&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/632783516/Lama_Carpaint_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761637160872&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"634388514\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Carpaint_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"632783516\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"beacab0c-7475-4b33-a753-4a8fa4a91102\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/632783516/Lama_Carpaint_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761637160872&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/632783516/Lama_Carpaint_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761637160872&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>In this lesson, you’ll learn how to make Solid (non-metallic) and Metallic Car paints in Lama.  This knowledge can also be applied to many other metallic and non-metallic materials, too!</p><p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"900639ab-c2a2-470c-bff3-35428cafdbe4\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Many thanks to BAC for letting us use their model of the incredible <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.bac-mono.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MonoR</a></p></div></div><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"07c01fbe-5ae2-4238-b65a-87f5020a3207\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Non-Metallic Lama Car paints</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"3d031ffb-f393-4480-aa2b-75e5fc1414dc\" data-macro-id=\"2be523df6598b69b63ee304601cd30a96d477e2e3b0d3273a647b559decdc5df\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1130821887\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"mono1.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/632783516/mono1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761553659209&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=760\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/632783516/mono1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761553659209&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-w